data.description: Time for some apple pie! Get inside as soon as possible, so you can start picking apples, making pie, and relaxing on the Trex deck. The aesthetic appeal of this expansive residence is much enhanced after its recent application of fresh paint. The kitchen, living, and dining rooms have a warm, light, and inviting ambiance, owing to the abundance of windows, stunning wood flooring, and the high ceiling. The home has an additional family room with a walk-out basement. The top level has the master suite and three more bedrooms. Backing up to open space, this .47-acre property is located in Canyon Creek Estates. There's a park across the street, making this a perfect spot for your next home. The home boast two storage sheds, a two-car garage and a long driveway for those extra vehicles.  This is a must-see!
